'''單棘躄魚科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Chaunacidae}}<ref>{{FishBase family | family = Chaunacidae | month = February | year = 2006}}</ref>）是[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]][[鮟鱇目|鮟鱇目]]'''單棘躄魚亞目'''中的唯一一科，英文俗名為「Sea toads（意思為「海[[蟾蜍|蟾蜍]]」）」及「Coffinfishes（意思為「[[棺材|棺材]]魚」）」，中文俗名則常稱之為「五腳虎」。

單棘躄魚科的物種為棲息於[[太平洋|太平洋]]、[[印度洋|印度洋]]與[[大西洋|大西洋]][[大陸坡|大陸坡]]上的深海魚<ref name=EoF>{{cite book |editor=Paxton, J.R. |editor2=Eschmeyer, W.N.|author1=Bertelsen, E.  |author2=Pietsch, T.W. |lastauthoramp=yes |year=1998|title=Encyclopedia of Fishes|publisher= Academic Press|location=San Diego|pages= 140|isbn= 0-12-547665-5}}</ref>，深度最深可達 {{convert|2460|m|abbr=on}} ，其中{{link-en|槳躄魚屬|Chaunacops}}物種的棲息深度多半高於{{link-en|單棘躄魚屬|Chaunax}}物種。

身體呈卵圓形，尾柄短，身體佈滿棘刺狀的細鱗，體型最大可達 {{convert|30|cm|in|abbr=on}}。[[背鰭|背鰭]]第一鰭條演化為可進行[[生物發光|生物發光]]的吻觸手，懸吊在口上方。口裂大，呈垂直狀。[[體側線|體側線]]的感覺溝清晰可見<ref>{{cite web | url = http://tolweb.org/Chaunacidae | author = John H. Caruso | title = Chaunacidae | publisher = Tree of Life web project | year = 2005 | accessdate = 3 April 2006 | archive-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201215225641/http://tolweb.org/Chaunacidae | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[胸鰭|胸鰭]]演化成類似[[足|足]]的構造，可在[[海床|海床]]上爬行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://oceanexplorer.noaa.gov/okeanos/explorations/ex1502/logs/apr13/apr13.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-07-03 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020224458/https://oceanexplorer.noaa.gov/okeanos/explorations/ex1502/logs/apr13/apr13.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Sea_toad_(Chaunacops_cf._melanostomus).jpg|thumb]]（Chaunacops melanostomus）]]
==分類==
'''單棘躄魚科'''下分2個屬，如下：
*{{link-en|槳躄魚屬|Chaunacops}}(''Chaunacops'')
**[[印度洋槳躄魚|印度洋槳躄魚]](''Chaunacops coloratus'') <small>[[Samuel_Garman|Garman]], 1899</small>
**[[黑口槳躄魚|黑口槳躄魚]](''Chaunacops melanostomus'') <small>[[John_H._Caruso|J. H. Caruso]], 1989</small>
**[[玫瑰槳躄魚|玫瑰槳躄魚]](''Chaunacops roseus'') <small>[[Thomas_Barbour|T. Barbour]], 1941</small>
**[[多棘深躄魚|多棘深躄魚]](''Chaunacops spinosus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Mark_A._McGrouther|McGrouther]], 2015</small><ref name=Ho2015>Ho, H.-C. & McGrouther, M. (2015): A new anglerfish from eastern Australia and New Caledonia (Lophiiformes: Chaunacidae: ''Chaunacops''), with new data and submersible observation of ''Chaunacops melanostomus''. ''Journal of Fish Biology, 86 (3): 940–951.''</ref>
*{{link-en|單棘躄魚屬|Chaunax}}(''Chaunax'')
**[[阿部單棘躄魚|阿部單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax abei'') <small>[[Yseult_Le_Danois|Y. Le Danois]], 1978</small>
**[[非洲單棘躄魚|非洲單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax africanus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Peter_Robert_Last|Last]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013>Ho, H.-C. & Last, P.R. (2013): Two new species of the coffinfish genus ''Chaunax'' (Lophiiformes: Chaunacidae) from the Indian Ocean. ''Zootaxa, 3710 (5): 436–448.''</ref>
**''[[Chaunax_apus|Chaunax apus]]'' <small>[[Richard_E._Lloyd|Lloyd]], 1909</small><ref name=Ho2015/>
**[[深南單棘躄魚|深南單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax atimovatae'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Ma_Wen-Chun_(biologist)|W. C. Ma]], 2016</small><ref name=Ho2016a>Ho, H.-C. & Ma, W.-C. (2016): Revision of southern African species of the anglerfish genus ''Chaunax'' (Lophiiformes: Chaunacidae), with descriptions of three new species. ''Zootaxa, 4144 (2): 175–194.''</ref>
**[[短體單棘躄魚|短體單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax brachysomus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Toshio_Kawai|Kawai]] & [[Fayakun_Satria|Satria]], 2015</small><ref name=Ho2015/>
**[[短輻單棘躄魚|短輻單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax breviradius'') <small>[[Yseult_Le_Danois|Y. Le Danois]], 1978</small>
**[[恩氏單棘躄魚|恩氏單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax endeavouri'') <small>[[Gilbert_Percy_Whitley|Whitley]], 1929</small>
**[[單棘躄魚|單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax fimbriatus'') <small>[[Franz_Martin_Hilgendorf|Hilgendorf]], 1879</small>
**[[火焰單棘躄魚|火焰單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax flammeus'') <small>[[Yseult_Le_Danois|Y. Le Danois]], 1979</small>
**[[黃斑單棘躄魚|黃斑單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax flavomaculatus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Clive_D._Roberts|C. D. Roberts]] & [[Andrew_L._Stewart|A. L. Stewart]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013a>Ho, H.-C., Roberts, C.D. & Stewart, A.L. (2013): [http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2013/f/zt03620p111.pdf A review of the anglerfish genus ''Chaunax'' (Lophiiformes: Chaunacidae) from New Zealand and adjacent waters, with descriptions of four new species.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2013/f/zt03620p111.pdf |date=20200621000413 }} ''Zootaxa, 3620 (1): 89–111.''</ref>
**[[白腹單棘躄魚|白腹單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax gomoni'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Toshio_Kawai|Kawai]] & [[Fayakun_Satria|Satria]], 2015</small><ref name=Ho2015/>
**[[南非單棘躄魚|南非單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax heemstraorum'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Ma_Wen-Chun_(biologist)|W. C. Ma]], 2016</small><ref name=Ho2016a/>
**[[何氏單棘躄魚|何氏單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax hollemani'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Ma_Wen-Chun_(biologist)|W. C. Ma]], 2016</small><ref name=Ho2016a/>
**[[側斑單棘躄魚|側斑單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax latipunctatus'') <small>[[Yseult_Le_Danois|Y. Le Danois]], 1984</small>
**[[紅鞋單棘躄魚|紅鞋單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax mulleus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Clive_D._Roberts|C. D. Roberts]] & [[Andrew_L._Stewart|A. L. Stewart]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013a/>
**[[印度單棘躄魚|印度單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax multilepis'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Rajeesh_Kumar_Meleppura|Meleppura]] & [[Kinattum_Kara_Bineesh|Bineesh]], 2016</small><ref name=Ho2016>Ho, H.-C., Meleppura, R.K. & Bineesh, K.K. (2016): ''Chaunax multilepis'' sp. nov., a new species of ''Chaunax'' (Lophiiformes: Chaunacidae) from the northern Indian Ocean. ''Zootaxa, 4103 (2): 130-136.''</ref>
**[[雲紋單棘躄魚|雲紋單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax nebulosus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Peter_Robert_Last|Last]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013/>
**[[裸腹單棘躄魚|裸腹單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax nudiventer'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]] & [[Shao_Kwang-Tsao|K. T. Shao]], 2010</small>
**[[雲紋單棘躄魚|雲紋單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax penicillatus'') <small>[[Allan_Riverstone_McCulloch|McCulloch]], 1915</small>
**[[圓頭單棘躄魚|圓頭單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax pictus'') <small>[[Richard_Thomas_Lowe|R. T. Lowe]], 1846</small>
**[[網紋單棘躄魚|網紋單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax reticulatus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Clive_D._Roberts|C. D. Roberts]] & [[Andrew_L._Stewart|A. L. Stewart]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013a/>
**[[紅衣單棘躄魚|紅衣單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax russatus'') <small>[[何宣慶|H. C. Ho]], [[Clive_D._Roberts|C. D. Roberts]] & [[Andrew_L._Stewart|A. L. Stewart]], 2013</small><ref name=Ho2013a/>
**[[斑點單棘躄魚|斑點單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax stigmaeus'') <small>[[Henry_Weed_Fowler|Fowler]], 1946</small>
**[[薩氏單棘躄魚|薩氏單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax suttkusi'') <small>[[John_H._Caruso|J. H. Caruso]], 1989</small>
**[[蔭單棘躄魚|蔭單棘躄魚]](''Chaunax umbrinus'') <small>[[Charles_Henry_Gilbert|C. H. Gilbert]], 1905</small>

